<a name="suicide"> </a>
You are right, whoever wrote this letter is a
fake.  This story is so improbable, that I had to
believe it was one of those Urban Legends.  One beer
and you are dead.  What was in that beer &#8212; snake
venom?  How many AA's die under the errogenous
direction of doctors?  Well in my 20-some year
experience with mental health types, I have never
heard of a death coming from a doctor convincing
